OL,4,Cduring match calls for coroner's
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FSteve was watching at home when the
OL,8,Fcommentary team said there was a
OL,9,Fcommotion in the away end and a fan
OL,10,Fappeared to be very ill. He hoped the
OL,11,Ffan would be OK and then his phone
OL,12,Frang.
OL,14,F"It's my son Matthew telling me that
OL,15,Fmy brother, his uncle, has collapsed
OL,16,Fand he's not breathing. I could hear
OL,17,Fall this going on in the background
OL,18,Fpeople shouting asking for help, I
OL,19,Fcould even hear the crowd saying 'stop
OL,20,Fthe game, stop the game'."
