OL,7,F"I could hear the crowd going 'stop
OL,8,Fthe game'"
OL,10,FThe game wasn't stopped but an off-
OL,11,Fduty paramedic who was watching Albion
OL,12,Fstepped into help. Steve says it took
OL,13,F10-12 minutes before the stadium's
OL,14,Fmedics and a defibrillator arrived.
