OL,7,F"I've heard from numerous fans who
OL,8,Fwere in close proximity. I could hear
OL,9,Fthem screaming for assistance and for
OL,10,Fit to take 10 minutes in this day and
OL,11,Fage, it shouldn't happen. One of those
OL,12,Fstewards should've been trained, it
OL,13,Fshouldn't take someone from the
OL,14,Ftravelling contingent in a tier below
OL,15,Fto come up the stairs and start
OL,16,Fadministering first aid."
