OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FSteve wants a Coroner's Inquest to
OL,8,Ffind out the full details of what
OL,9,Fhappened and for a review across the
OL,10,Fcountry of how football stadiums
OL,11,Frespond to medical emergencies like
OL,12,Fthis.
OL,14,F"Something needs to be seriously
OL,15,Flooked at in the failings that have
OL,16,Fhappened at Hillsborough and I'm
OL,17,Fsaying that as a football fan, not
OL,18,Fjust someone that's lost his brother."
