OL,7,FI ask if he's heard anything
OL,8,Freassuring from Sheffield Wednesday
OL,9,Fsince.
OL,11,F"Nothing, nothing at all and that
OL,12,Ftells me everything I need to know
OL,13,Fabout the club. I've had lots of well
OL,14,Fwishes from Wednesday fans but nothing
OL,15,Ffrom official sources of Sheffield
OL,16,FWednesday."
OL,18,F"Something needs to be seriously
OL,19,Flooked at in the failings at
OL,20,FHillsborough"
