OL,7,F"I've always thought the Albion were a
OL,8,Ffamily club and they reaffirmed that
OL,9,Fwith authority last night. We felt
OL,10,Flike part of a family, we felt like
OL,11,Fwe'd known them for years."
OL,13,FHis energy is now going into
OL,14,Fsupporting his relatives and fighting
OL,15,Ffor change after what happened to his
OL,16,Fbrother.
