OL,3,CBrother of football fan who died
OL,4,Cduring match calls for coroner's
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"I will be pushing as hard as I can
OL,8,Ffor the inquiry that I feel is needed,
OL,9,Fhow long that will take I don't know
OL,10,Fbut I'm in for the long haul on it to
OL,11,Fget a bit of justice for my brother
OL,12,Fand to make sure that no other
OL,13,Ffootball fan has to go through what
OL,14,Fwe're going through."
