OL,7,FSheffield Wednesday referred us to the
OL,8,Fstatement they released at the
OL,9,Fweekend: "First and foremost, the
OL,10,Fthoughts of everyone at Sheffield
OL,11,FWednesday remain with the loved ones
OL,12,Fof Mr Townsend and the wider West
OL,13,FBromwich Albion community.
OL,15,F"The club continue to liaise with West
OL,16,FBromwich Albion and all relevant
OL,17,Fparties as we collectively establish
OL,18,Fthe full circumstances regarding this
OL,19,Ftragic loss of life."
