OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Sports Grounds
OL,8,FSafety Authority (SGSA) said: "We are
OL,9,Fdeeply saddened by the tragic death of
OL,10,Fthe spectator at the Sheffield
OL,11,FWednesday v West Brom match on the
OL,12,Fweekend, and our condolences are with
OL,13,Fhis family and friends at this time.
OL,15,F"Ensuring spectator safety at sports
OL,16,Fground is the priority for the SGSA.
OL,17,FIn 2022, the SGSA published guidance
OL,18,Fwhich provides stadium safety teams
OL,19,Fwith considerations for dealing with
OL,20,Fmedical incidents that occur in the
OL,21,Fcrowd.
